content.rendered:
Directed by Tinu Suresh Desai.

Written by Tanya Pathak. Girish Dhamija. Vikram Bhatt.

Cast Sharman Joshi(Jai Singh Gujjar). Meera Chopra(Shivangi). Vishal Karwal(Veer). Surendra Pal(Shivangi’s Father (as Surender Pal)). Charu Rohatgi(Shivangi’s Mother (as Charu Rohatagi)). Sushmita Mukherjee(Kesar Maa (as Sushmita Mukharji)). Siraj Mustafa Khan(Rana Jag Pratap Singh (as Siraj Mustufa)). Jalpa Bhatt(Bua). Jagat Rawat(Kaka). Vishal Malhotra(Surya Pratap). Dinesh Mehta(Rudra Pratap (as Dinesh Mahta)). Kamal Adib(Pratap Singh (as Kamal Adip)). Jyoti Chudasma(Possessed Girl Mother). Mansi(Possessed Girl). Sujay Hulchal(Sharman’s Lawyer). Vipin Sharma(Shivangi’s Lawyer). Meenal Kapoor(Dayan). Arun Bali(Guruji). Gajendra Chauhan(Tantrik Baba). Tony Goodall(Doctor). Danielle Parton(Nurse). Tracie Diane(Mysterious Old Woman). Velton Lishke(Shivangi’s Driver (as Goerge)) . Robin George(Train Passenger (uncredited)). Amir Malik(Shivangi’s Step Brother (uncredited)). Anna-Maria Wiktorsson(Tourist in London (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Sada Bhuvad. Santosh Kumar Jha. Firuzi Khan. Cyrus Patel. Sandeep Shandilya. Roshan Singh.

Production 1920 London.
